(y) 25 2 placeTR
(y = ) -36 -25 placeBR
(c) -36 -21 placeBL
1 -3 rmoveto
(j) show
0 3 rmoveto
SYM ( - ) show
TI (r) show
(q) -26 -35 placeBL 
