TI (c) show 
(q) -30 -79 placeBR

gsave
27 rotate
TI (px + qy + r = c) 20 -60 placeBL
1 -3 rmoveto
(j) show
(px + qy + r = c) 10 -83 placeBL
1 -3 rmoveto
(j) show
SYM ( + 1) show
TI (px + qy + r = c) 0 -106 placeBL
1 -3 rmoveto
(j) show
SYM ( + 2) show
-27 rotate
grestore


